2052.subject: TAT
2052.descrlong: Provides overview of technical and production support for live productions, capstones, staged readings, and projects produced by TAT. Provides experience in supporting, mounting, and crewing productions. Introduction to set design and construction, lighting design, props, makeup, sound design, crewing shows as stage hands, stage management, production assisting, production organization, and related technical support areas. (Offered fall semester.)
